#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#: _posts/2023-05-04-quarkus-3-0-2-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Quarkus 3.0.2.Final released - Maintenance release"
msgstr "Quarkus 3.0.2.Final发布 - 维护性发布"

#. type: YAML Front Matter: synopsis
#: _posts/2023-05-04-quarkus-3-0-2-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Quarkus 3.0.2.Final is the first maintenance release of our 3.0 release train."
msgstr "Quarkus 3.0.2.Final是我们3.0版本列车的第一个维护版本。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2023-05-04-quarkus-3-0-2-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We released Quarkus 3.0.2.Final, the first maintenance release of our 3.0 release train (as our first public release for 3.0 was 3.0.1.Final)."
msgstr "我们发布了Quarkus 3.0.2.Final，这是我们3.0版本列车的第一个维护版本（因为我们3.0的第一个公开版本是3.0.1.Final）。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2023-05-04-quarkus-3-0-2-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "As usual, it contains bugfixes and documentation improvements."
msgstr "像往常一样，它包含错误修复和文档改进。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2023-05-04-quarkus-3-0-2-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "It should be a safe upgrade for anyone already using 3.0."
msgstr "对于已经使用3.0的人来说，这应该是一次安全的升级。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2023-05-04-quarkus-3-0-2-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you are not already using 3.0, please refer to https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-0-final-released/[the Quarkus 3.0 announcement] and in particular the section about the https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-0-final-released/#upgrading[upgrade path to 3.0]."
msgstr "如果你还没有使用3.0，请参考 link:https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-0-final-released/[Quarkus 3.0公告] ，特别是关于 link:https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-0-final-released/#upgrading[升级到3.0的路径] 部分。"

